            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>广汽埃安（AION）宣布登陆香港市场，首家陈列室日前开幕。品牌同日发布了旗下全新纯电动车 AION Y Plus ，庆祝埃安九龙湾陈列室开幕。广汽埃安同场亦展示了 AION ES。现在就让小编带大家先睹为快，看看广汽埃安这 2 部右軚车吧。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217740" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128155807-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新开业的埃安九龙湾陈列室位于九龙东商业大厦「第一集团中心」，毗邻大型商场和邮轮码头，其设计以简约、时尚风格为主。陈列室内还设有新能源充电展示区，帮助客户了解充电配套设备及如何充电操作。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217744" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160654-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217743" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128180533-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新能源充电展示区</p><h2>AION Y Plus</h2><p>广汽埃安表示，旗下 AION Y Plus 将会于今年 5 月正式进入香港市场。AION Y Plus 定位是「科技头等舱」，NEDC 标准续航里程为 490KM。是次在陈列室展出的是右軚版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217741" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160623-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217742" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160635-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217753" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420769369_3827754243.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>广汽埃安亦照顾到消费者对车内储物空间的需求，AION Y Plus 后备箱空间十足，能够轻松放入 3 个大行李箱。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217751" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420726932_2437775233.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217754" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421104684_9085122975.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>如果对露营有兴趣的朋友也可以考虑这辆车，AION 方面表示这辆车可以搬走整个露营营地，符合露营爱好者需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217752" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420845676_9073389444.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>规格</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 294px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">基本规格</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">长 × 宽 × 高（mm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">4535 × 1870 × 1650</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">轴距（mm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">2750 mm</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">座位</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">5</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">最大功率（kW）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">150 kW</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">最大扭距（Nm）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">225Nm</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">电池类型</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">磷酸铁锂电池</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">电池能量（kWh）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">61.5 kWh</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">续航里程（km）（NEDC 标准）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">NEDC：490 km</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">转向系统</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">电动助力转向系统（EPS）</td></tr><tr style="height: 54px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 54px;">悬挂系统</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 54px; text-align: center;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 100%;">前：麦花臣式独立悬挂系统</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">后：扭力杆悬挂系统</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 144px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 100%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">外饰</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">17 吋，铝合金轮圈</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外后视镜电动调节</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">LED 大灯</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外后视镜电动折叠</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">LED 日间行车灯</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外后视镜发热功能</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">后雾灯</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">电动隐藏式门把手</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">外后视镜集成转向灯</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"></td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 288px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">内饰</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">I PEDAL 电子踏板</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">多功能軚盘</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">无钥匙进入</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">优质仿真皮座椅</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">10.25 吋液晶仪表</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">司机席电动座椅</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">14.63 吋触控中控萤幕</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">四门车窗一触式升降功能（带防夹功能）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">车载音响系统（支援英文、繁体中文及不同语言）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">全景天窗（带电动遮阳帘）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">手机蓝牙连接</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">司机座椅靠背可完全放平</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">6 扬声器 Bongiovi 大师品牌音效</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">第二排座椅 40/60 折叠全放平</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">自动空调</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">32 种颜色车厢氛围灯</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">PM 2.5 滤网</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排 12V 电源</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">后排空调出风口</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前／后排 USB 接口</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">优质仿真皮軚盘</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">内后视镜头带 USB 接口（5V）</td></tr></tbody></table><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 240px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 100%; height: 24px;" colspan="2">安全</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">后备轮胎</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排安全带未扣灯光提示及声响</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">防锁死制动系统（ABS）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">ISOFIX 儿童座椅接口号</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">电子车身稳定系统（ESP）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">自动驻车 Auto Hold</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">电子制动力分配（EBD）</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">牵引力控制系统（TCS）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">制动能量回收系统</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">胎压监测系统</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排双安全气囊</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">定速巡航</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排侧气囊</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">倒车雷达（后雷达）</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">侧气帘</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">360° 高清全景泊车</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">前排限力式安全带</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"></td></tr></tbody></table><h2></h2><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/26/xiaomi-su7-ev-28-dec-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">官方微博开启车章曝光，小米 SU7 电动车 28/12 发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/toyota-recalled-bz3-ev-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">剩余电量显示比实际高，一汽丰田召回 2.5 万部安全隐患 bZ3 电动车</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">仁孚引入两款全新 smart #1 电动车，预计 2024 年首季可正式交付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>AION ES</h2><p>广汽埃安亦展出了另一款右軚版本 AION ES。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217756" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/420502410_7850599467.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>AION ES 是广汽埃安针对出行市场的特供车，使用 136 马力电动机，电池容量为 50.6kWh，一次充电续航里程可达 442 公里（NEDC）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217757" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/421023911_1304094856.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>同场加映：Hyper SSR</h2><p>陈列室开业当天，除了新的右軚版本 AION Y Plus 及 AION Es 外，广汽埃安亦于同场展出 Hyper SSR。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217748" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160748-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hyper SSR</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1217759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/20240128160834-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Hyper SSR</p><p>Hyper SSR 是埃安旗下高级豪华车系 Hyper （昊铂）的首款车型，拥有前 1 后 2 三电机，电驱峰值总功率达 900kW，采用前后双叉臂悬架，实现极致操控性和乘坐舒适性。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/26/xiaomi-su7-ev-28-dec-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">官方微博开启车章曝光，小米 SU7 电动车 28/12 发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/23/toyota-recalled-bz3-ev-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">剩余电量显示比实际高，一汽丰田召回 2.5 万部安全隐患 bZ3 电动车</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">仁孚引入两款全新 smart #1 电动车，预计 2024 年首季可正式交付</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/29/gac-aion/life-tech/auto/">广汽 AION 强势袭港　Y Plus、ES 右軚版双杰打响头炮</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
